### AI Routes Test File
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AI CLASSIFICATION
### ============================================

### Classify Photo
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/classify-photo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "base64Image": "/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQEAYABgAAD...",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg"
}

### ============================================
### DUPLICATE DETECTION
### ============================================

### Check for Duplicates
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/check-duplicate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "REPORT_UUID_HERE"
}

### ============================================
### CHATBOT
### ============================================

### Chatbot - Simple Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Bagaimana cara melaporkan jalan rusak?",
  "history": []
}

### Chatbot - With History
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Berapa lama prosesnya?",
  "history": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Bagaimana cara melaporkan jalan rusak?"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Anda bisa melaporkan jalan rusak melalui aplikasi Laporin dengan mengisi formulir laporan dan mengunggah foto kerusakan."
    }
  ]
}

### Chatbot - Streaming Response
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apa saja kategori laporan yang tersedia?",
  "history": []
}

### ============================================
### AI SUGGESTIONS (Requires Auth)
### ============================================

### Get Report Suggestions
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/suggestions?reportId=REPORT_UUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

