  "mimeType": "image/png"
}

### Example: Common Chatbot Questions

### Question 1: How to report
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Bagaimana cara membuat laporan?",
  "history": []
}

### Question 2: Report status
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Bagaimana cara mengecek status laporan saya?",
  "history": []
}

### Question 3: Categories
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apa saja jenis kerusakan yang bisa dilaporkan?",
  "history": []
}

### Question 4: Anonymous reporting
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apakah bisa melaporkan tanpa login?",
  "history": []
}

### Question 5: Response time
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Berapa lama laporan akan ditanggapi?",
  "history": []
}
